<!--
# Long Running - Multi-Step Actions as Futures

With async actions, "long running" is simply a future that takes a while to
resolve. `<Patrol>` loops several times with a delay between steps, then a final
log. `{RunOnLoad}` runs the sequence on load, then exits.

    beet --main=examples/action/long_running.bsx
-->
<Sequence {RunOnLoad}>
	<Patrol/>
	<Log::Message("patrol complete")/>
</Sequence>
